data.description: Home sits on 1 acre with trees and privacy. Large living room with wood burning fireplace- accent wall also.Vaulted ceiling with beam gives the house character. Baywindow brings in natural lighting. Kitchen has eat in bar, tile back splash. Seperate dining room- or could be a home office, with hard wood floors. Laundry room. Good size bedrooms. Linen closet in hallway. Primary bedroom & bathroom- bath is updated with tile walk in shower, new vanity & toilet & flooring. Side entry to kitchen. Double attached carport. Outside storage room. Back yard is large, fenced with some trees. Extra parking. Separate detached garage- could be converted into a inlaw suite.Roll up door, 2 side entry doors. Unrestricted and no HOA. Buyer or Buyers agent to verify all information deemed important.
